Concept	Meaning

Memory	Stores past messages

BufferMemory	Stores entire conversation

WindowMemory	Only last N messages

EntityMemory	Extracts and stores entities

RetrieverMemory	Stores in vector store

Memory in LC	Controls what LLM sees each turn

